Advantages of maven
1) Quick project setup
    a) Maven bring conventions over configuration, thus reducing setup time
2) Projects are modular
3) Mature dependency management
4) Mature project build lifecycle
5) Robust plugin community

Dis Advantages of Maven
1) Projects are described in XML document, contrained by XML schema
    a) some consider XML dated
2) Gradle uses a Groovy DSL, which can offer greated build flexibility
    a) Rare the additional flexibility is needed

